👉 Think:

Not data rows → decision-grade assets

⸻

🔐 Zone F — Vault & Backup (The Reserve)

Purpose: long-term storage + replay

Features:
	•	Immutable ledger (append-only)
	•	Versioned datasets (time snapshots)
	•	Cold storage tiers
	•	Rehydration capability (re-run models with new context)

Pantheon mapping:
	•	Checksum + Mother Duck
	•	Hermit Crab (provenance shells)

