⚖️ Zone G — Governance & Ethics (The Control Room)

Purpose: ensure system doesn’t become predatory

Controls:
	•	ΣC scoring (allow / degrade / deny)
	•	Reversibility (user can reset/delete)
	•	Consent tracking
	•	Audit logs

Pantheon mapping:
	•	Arctic Framework
	•	Badger (CAO) → attention protection

